{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Device_orientation_events\">Device orientation events <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>构造函数</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><em><code>acceleration</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>accelerationIncludingGravity</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>interval</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>rotationRate</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Device Orientation Events 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventAcceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEventAcceleration</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventRotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEventRotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>acceleration 属性会返回设备的加速度记录（单位：<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m / s2</a>）。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 如果硬件无法从 acceleration 数据中移除重力加速度，则该值在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a>中可能并不存在，你应当使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity</code></a>代替</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">var acceleration = instanceOfDeviceMotionEvent.acceleration;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值","title":"值","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>acceleration</code>是一个包括三轴（x、y、z）加速度信息的对象，每个轴都有自己的属性：</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"x\"><code>x</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示 x 轴（西到东）上的加速度</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"y\"><code>y</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示 y 轴（南到北）上的加速度</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"z\"><code>z</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示 z 轴（下到上）上的加速度</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"说明","id":"说明","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/deviceorientation/#ref-for-dom-devicemotionevent-acceleration③","title":"DeviceOrientation Event Specification"}],"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"推荐浏览","title":"推荐浏览","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity</code></a></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/devicemotion_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">devicemotion (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/devicemotion_event\"><code>window.ondevicemotion</code></a></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/deviceorientation_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">deviceorientation (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Device_orientation_events/Detecting_device_orientation\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Detecting device orientation (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/Orientation_and_motion_data_explained\">Orientation and motion data explained</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"值","id":"值"},{"text":"说明","id":"说明"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"推荐浏览","id":"推荐浏览"}],"summary":"acceleration 属性会返回设备的加速度记录（单位：m / s2）。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/devicemotionevent/acceleration","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/devicemotionevent/acceleration/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent","title":"DeviceMotionEvent"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration","title":"DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration"}],"pageTitle":"DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}